      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i need some help writing an email. We have a candidate for a Senior DevOps role here in our Austin office who made it all the way to the final round, but we decided to go with someone else because they had more experience with Kubernetes orchestration. The candidate was actually really great—super smart and had a really positive attitude—so i don't want the email to feel cold, but i need it to be professional and firm so they know the decision is final. Can you help me draft that?",
